\int_{0}^{1} df(\gamma(t))\cdot\dot{\gamma}(t)\,dt = \int_{0}^{1} \frac{d}{dt}(f \circ \gamma)(t)\,dt = f(\gamma(1)) - f(\gamma(0)) = f(x_1, x_2) - f(0,0).
\gamma_1 (1) = (x_1,0) = \gamma_2 (0)
